    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introdução a Test::File::ShareDir</title>

      <para>
        Test::File::ShareDir is some low level plumbing to enable a distribution to
perform tests while consuming its own share directories in a manner similar
to how they will be once installed. This allows <xref
linkend="perl-file-sharedir"/> to see the latest version of content instead
of whatever is installed on the target system where you are testing.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

